Enum EventSource.UIEvent

EventSource
public static enum EventSource.UIEvent
extends Enum<EventSource.UIEvent>

These event constants are used for communication with the user interface. They generally describe device connection events rather than data events although data events can also be communicated to the user interface in some circumstances. They are one-off events (e.g. transitions), not states.

Enum Constant Summary
